rows.label: tlk70000017_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Those huge hulking things from before
were real beauties...

rows.label: tlk70000017_02_msg0002
rows.name:
They move so smoothly, you'd think
they were living things and not
machines at all! Hah ha!

rows.label: tlk70000017_02_msg0003
rows.name:
High-quality indeed... Such weight...
Such presence... I wonder who could
have crafted perfection of this ilk?

rows.label: tlk70000017_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Both in quality and quantity, they seem
to exceed the abilities of mere
mortals... A puzzle indeed.

rows.label: tlk70000017_02_msg0005
rows.name:
A divine power... Much like the
power of the Holy Grail...
